Incredibly, when you are received in a discriminatory and derogatory manner in any type of establishment, you must imagine the type of person who works, works or owns a business like this.

Well, we cannot let it go that an elderly lady (adult) who provided her service in this store as a salesperson or customer service and who was controlling the entry, to then serve the customers, gave us a deplorable and segregated welcome, characterized by making us feel discriminated against, by their gaze, gestures and explicitly belittling the fact that we could acquire any good.

For our part, we do not recommend this place at all, because despite being well located, its prices are not in line with the market, if we refer to the fact that most of what is offered can be found in other stores at a better price.

Although this situation was very uncomfortable, for us it will become just an anecdote. However, we are aware that unfortunately it can be a reality that is experienced daily.", 'Excellent store, very good service... concerned at all times to take good care of what we needed and we bought happily.', 'South American Chile🇨🇱 is also good', 'I always find something beautiful at Christmas and gifts', 'Very good service and excellent product']
